Hi @kimbologic ...I had this error too. Fixed it by updating interface definition in src/types/index.ts

`export interface Penalties {
  drawdown_threshold: number;
  risk_profile: number;
  total: number;
}`

and in src/components/Checkpoints/Checkpoints.tsx changed to:

`<SimpleGrid cols={5}>
          <PenaltyCard
              title="Penalties"
              penalties={{
                ...penalties,
                risk_profile: penalties.risk_profile ?? 1,
              }}
              tooltipText="Risk normalization multiplier, due to drawdown. Note that this term may be larger than one, indicating that the miner receives a boost in score due to minimal drawdown utilization."
            />
        </SimpleGrid>`

Cheers! 🙂

